{"type": "article", "id": 29763, "title": "地标灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-18T22:47:26Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 36, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160718175946b3lLO2GFoM0rgI7f.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>米兰和悉尼这两座城市的建筑轮廓在由 <a href=\"http://www.marianovozhilova.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maria Novozhilova</a> 设计的 All Around 灯具中变成了迷人抽象的柔光。几何形的设计使它能够以任意角度摆放，没有传统的顶部和底部限制，把两盏灯拼在一起还能组成一张小边桌，使用起来非常灵活。由细支架支撑的塑料灯罩上刻着两座城市的地标，在黑暗中透过灯光的照射能够营造出独特的气氛，延续人们对于城市的想象。如果你对这盏城市灯感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.marianovozhilova.com/all-around-lamp.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>中的邮箱进行订购。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607181800293je5v1F2mXkxdGca.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607181800294bfe2E1YwvuTDJt3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607181800305MDXqihQuU30Atyl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160718180030CvQegbLDZ0jsBcHN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.663333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}